## What This Module Does

The node registry provides a centralized manifest-based registry for all available node types (plugins, effects, generators). It discovers, validates, and catalogs node definitions from plugin manifests, providing a unified interface for the node graph UI to query available nodes and their capabilities.

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- Does not instantiate nodes (delegates to plugin loader)
- Does not manage node graph connections (delegates to node graph UI)
- Does not handle node execution (delegates to render engine)
- Does not provide UI components (delegates to P1-N4)

